flowchart LR
  subgraph Client[接入端]
    direction LR
    MP[微信小程序<br/>Taro]
    H5[用户 H5<br/>Taro H5]
    AdminWeb[后台 Web<br/>React + AntD]
  end

  subgraph Edge[接入层]
    direction TB
    APIGW[API 入口<br/>NestJS Controller + Guard + Filter]
    Mock[Mock API（可选）<br/>Prism + Fixtures]
  end

  subgraph Monolith[应用层：模块化单体（apps/api）]
    direction TB
    AuthUser["身份与权限域<br/>auth / users / rbac / addresses"]
    Trading["交易主域<br/>patents / listings / orders / contracts / files"]
    ServiceDesk["客服与运营域<br/>conversations / cases / comments / notifications"]
    OpsDomain["运营扩展域<br/>reports / regions / config / patent-map / patent-maintenance / alerts / ai"]
    Common["通用支撑<br/>audit-log / idempotency / content-event / webhook"]
  end

  subgraph Data[数据与基础设施]
    direction LR
    PG[(PostgreSQL 16<br/>主交易库)]
    Redis[(Redis 7<br/>缓存/限流/任务队列)]
    Upload[(本地 uploads 目录<br/>开发与演示环境)]
    OSS[(对象存储 S3 兼容<br/>MinIO/COS/OSS)]
  end

  subgraph External[第三方能力]
    direction LR
    WxAuth[微信开放平台<br/>登录/消息]
    WxPay[微信支付 v3]
    MsgProvider[短信/邮件通道]
    AIProvider[AI 服务商（P1）]
  end

